def calculate_minimum_cost(B, W, X, Y, Z):
    b1 = B / X
    b2 = B * Y + B * Z
    w1 = W * Y
    w2 = W * X + Z * W
    min_cost_black = min(b1, b2)
    min_cost_white = min(w1, w2)
    return min_cost_black + min_cost_white
